    "doc://com.apple.documentation/videos/play/wwdc2019/221": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "text": "Meet PencilKit, Apple's feature-rich drawing and annotation framework. With just a few lines of code, you can add a full drawing experience to your app — with access to a canvas, responsive inks, rich tool palette and drawing model. Hear the technical details that make a great Apple Pencil experience. Learn about the new screenshot editor and how you can adopt just a few small APIs to enable your full content to be captured beyond the size of the screen, with or without your app's user interface.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/videos/play/wwdc2019/221",
